“The Commuter” (2018) stars Liam Neeson and Patrick Wilson with a strong supporting cast. It was directed by Jaume Collet-Serra marking the third time he has worked with Liam Neeson in the lead role. In simple terms, this is exactly what you would expect from a Liam Neeson action movie. Some things were done better, for example I found one of Liam’s best fight scenes to be in this movie using that seemingly one-shot style from Kingsman. Other stuff not so much like the cliche and overboard-ness if the final act. The characters of the movie were all serve-their-role sort of characters, not many dimensions beyond their niche of a role, save for Liam Neeson, who’s character had great setup with motives and personal drive within the third act making him a compelling and relatable character to back. The plot was good. Claustrophobic setting on the train was directed very well with some talented shots throughout the film. But the basic plot premise, to restate was like your typical Liam Neeson action movie. The spectacle was all solid or good till the third act where an abundance of CGI was used and honestly just looked cheap. Add cheap cgi to a predictable and cliche finale it detracts from the movie. All said and done, this was a fun movie. No it wasn’t groundbreaking, and yes it was a run of the mill Liam Neeson Action Movie, but it was a fun time and had a very promising start with the buildup in the first act, great followthrough in the second act getting into the meat of the movie... then no pun intended it kinda de-railed in the third act giving an ending and “twist” that was pretty expected. Overall, a good time. B #TheCommuter #LiamNeeson #Nonstop #2018 #MovieReviews #Actionmovie #train #commuter

THE COMMUTER; aka “Non-Stop” on a train. The movie stars type-casted Liam Neeson playing an old retired badass who has a loving family, but then an incident onboard insert vehicle, drives him to take matters into his own hands at the same time being set up by the bad guys. It’s basically the same story as Non-Stop (also starring Liam Neeson, and also directed by the same person; Jaume Collet-Serra) but this time, it’s on a train. It is a decent action movie to say the least, it has more of a thriller vibe than an action film, with some twists and turns here and there… you know how it is with this kind of genre. It’s more of a mystery film cause it’s more of finding a specific target with people being obstacles to you. The action scenes I really like too because of how self-contained it is, really giving the film more weight as they made us really feel the claustrophobia cause it just takes place in one train. I will admit, the opening sequence for this movie is one of my favourite parts of the film. I just like the montage and the film’s Score that accompanies it. Will have to say, @roquebanos’ music for the film I really like a lot. It has this really nice relaxing piano piece in the start, mixed with the orchestra, the music may sound minimalistic, but I think it works for an ordinary type of protagonist we follow. It’s an interesting movie to see in theatres, and I personally don’t think it was a waste of money. I think you guys might enjoy it, but just go into it with low expectations cause I did and in the end, I genuinely enjoyed it. In the end, it’s a familiar story that you’ve seen before in a Liam Neeson action movie, it’s just a very self-contained minimalistic action thriller film, that’s enjoyable. So I wanna pass on the question to you. Have you seen The Commuter and what did you think of it? I’d love to know your thoughts in the comments below. THE COMMUTER (2018), DE JAUME COLLET-SERRA Calificación: 7/10 Durante su trayecto habitual de vuelta a casa en tren, un hombre de negocios felizmente casado comienza a hablar con una misteriosa pasajera que le hace una propuesta de dinero, que lo llevará a estar envuelto en una conspiración criminal. El actor Liam Neeson regresa una vez más a la acción en este thriller de suspenso bien logrado, con escenas intensas y sobretodo, atrapantes. El film sucede completamente en los vagones de un tren por lo que los personajes son el punto fuerte. The Commuter está bien filmada y tiene una trama ingeniosa pero simple, que no da vueltas complicadas. It’s worth every penny to watch Liam in his last action movies I’m not expecting too much in this movie before i watch, but the result ? I really like it, the story is about a man in his 60 years trying to live happily with his family, but somethings happen in his way home in the commuter that he always ride almost 20 years working, The action is so spectacular and humanism, the story is kind a great to involve audience guessing what happen next ? Liam is one of my fav actor of all time, his act always fascinated 4 of 5 stars ―――――――――――――――――――――――――――- Ini sangat berharga setiap sen nya untuk menyaksikan Liam di film aksi terakhir nya Saya tidak mengharapkan sesuatu yang lebih dari film ini sebelum menonton nya, tapi hasilnya ? Saya sangat menyukainya, menceritakan tentang seorang pria di usia 60 tahun yang berusaha hidup bahagia bersama keluarganya, tetapi sesuatu terjadi di kereta yang dinaiki selama 20 tahun ketika ia hendak pulang dari tempat kerja nya, aksi yang sangat spektakuler dan manusiawi, cerita nya pun melibatkan penonton untuk mengetahui apa yang akan terjadi selanjutnya ? Liam adalah salah satu aktor kesukaan saya sepanjang masa, aksi nya selalu membuat terpesona Bintang 4 dari 5 . . . . . . . #moviereview #thecommuter #liamneeson #15

#temanku #sahabatku #adikkelasku di #sma6pekanbaru Sekarang #sma8pekanbaru Mengundang ku ke acara #weddingparty Ponakannya Timothy & Ella Karena Tina Laheba seorang #pendeta Maka Timo berkeinginan yang memberkati #pernikahan nya adalah #tante nya sendiri Tina beetugas di kota #palembang Di acara yang penuh #kehangatankeluarga ini aku kembali diingatkan dengan #vespa lama ku yang dulu sering bikin repot Bang Hendri, Bapaknya Timo, #malamminggu aku sowan ke rumah mereka waktu itu aku kelas dua SMA, pas pulangnya vespa mogok, turun tanganlah Bang Hendri memperbaiki. Sehingga sudah identik aku ini dengan vespa biru yang sering mogok itu "Riko yang vespa biru itu ya..." gitu Kak Agnes, Kak Yuni dan Novel mengingatku. Si Teo adiknya Timo juga repot nyari aku di #fesbuk melayani permintaan Tantenya Tina yang pengen ketemu aku beberapa hari yang lalu. Dan sore itu aku terima pesan di messenger, shock dengar Tina di Pku. Malam itu juga kami nonton film #thecommuter yang bikin aku nyungsep nyungsep karena keseruan filmnya. Scene scene nya banyak yang bikin ngilu, tak sadar terpegang tangan Si Tina, ibarat nonton #filmhoror dimana kita butuh sesuaru untuk menutup muka saking takutnya. Pas pulang nonton kita ketawa bareng mengingat kejadian di studio. Ini semua hanya bisa kita lakukan bersama teman dan sahabat saja. "Oooh ini, Om Riko, yang aku disuruh cari di fesbuk..." kata Teo tadi pas aku menyalaminya. Karena mereka #orangmanado yang #kitasamuabasudara ada acara dansanya yaitu Polomais. Seru lho acara wedding partynya Timo & Ella. Ada booth coffee dan baristanya pula. Keren! Dan ada ajakan dari Tina ke #negeriatasawan #wayrebo di #nusatenggaratimur di kala hari jadinya yang ke #45tahun Tina pengen ngerayain di situ. Hebatnya rencana Bu Pendeta ini! Jika benar aku kan mendaki #gununhrinjani kelak di bulan Agustus atau #akhirbulanjuli maka aku akan ke sana. Thanks, Tina! Inshaa ALLAH...

6.5/10 Liam Neeson has become a film genre unto himself. The Commuter, directed by Jaume Collet-Serra, follows the footsteps of the many action thrillers Neeson has been in such as Unknown and Non-Stop. The plot, which doesn’t really add up, is very basic and quite unoriginal. But when we watch these kind of movies, we’re looking for over-the-top action scenes and a fun time, nothing more. #TheCommuter (2018) Insurance salesman Michael is on his daily commute home, which quickly becomes anything but routine. After being contacted by a mysterious stranger, Michael is forced to uncover the identity of a hidden passenger on the train before the last stop. As he works against the clock to solve the puzzle, he realizes a deadly plan is unfolding, and he is unwittingly caught up in a criminal conspiracy that carries life and death stakes for everyone on the train.

Sutradara: Jaume Colle Penulis: Byron Willi, Philip de B Bintang Film: Vera Farmiga, Liam Neeson, Patrick Wilson Genre: Action, Crime, Drama Tanggal Rilis: 2018-01-12 Plot Film The Commuter ini merupakan sebuah film terbaru 2018 asal Hollywood. Film ini memiliki genre baru Drama, Mystery, dan Thrilller, untuk sutradaranya akan disutradarai oleh Jauma Colet-Serra, untuk penulis naskah skenario dikuasai oleh Byron Willinger (Screenplay), dan Philip de Blasi. Film ini akan dibintangi para aktor-aktor terkenal di papan atas Hollywood yang akan berperan yaitu Vera Farmiga, Liam Neeson (aktor Utama), Patrick Wilson, Sam Neill, Elizabeth Mc Govern. diawal perilisan perdana film ini menggunakan bahasa Inggris bahasa utama dibioskop kesayangan anda. Sementara film ini akan digarap oleh rumah produksi Ombra Film, Studio Canal. dan The Picture Company. dan dinaungi distributor Lionsgate, VVS Films. Film ini masih menelusuri panjang durasi. Untuk The Picture Company akan merencanakan perilisan perdana pada tanggal 12 Januari (2018) (USA). . Sinopsis Film Film The Commuter ini akan menceritakan tentang seorang pria bernama Liam Veeson, dia adalah seorang pebisnis terkenal yang selalu disibukkan dengan aktivitas yang dihampiri setiap hari. Dari sinilah ketegangan dalam film ini akan dimulai Liam Neeson berada pada situasi yang sangat menegangkan, jika ia tidak melakukan apapun kereta akan mengalami kecelakaan dan nyawa ribuan orang pun terancam. Ia pun harus menggagalkan sesuatu untuk menggagalkan aksinya. Kemudian hari, sebuah peristiwa terjadi didalam Commuter dan pria menjadi aksi saksi terjadinya konpirasi kriminal ketika pulang dari kantornya tersebut. Mengetahui sebuah rencana tan pa sengaja dari sekelompok orang berniat untuk menghancurkan kereta. Disisi lain Neeson harus melakukan guna menghentikan kejahatan tersebut, karena jika sempaikereta ceoat mengalami kecelakaan peritiwwa orang ingin menghancurkan kereta cepat tersebut. Bagi yang penasaran dengan kisah kelanjutan kisahnya, The Commuter akan dirilis perdana menjelang tahun 2018, masih cukup lama Sutradara Jaume Collet-Serra ini akan dirilis pada tanggal 12 Januari (2018) (USA). . #neracafilm #thecommuter

(Listen / download) That Film Stew Ep 103 - The Commuter Review (LINK IN BIO) The action thriller The Commuter is directed by Jaume Collet-Serra, and stars Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga, Patrick Wilson, Jonathan Banks, Elizabeth McGovern, and Sam Neil. Thanks to Anarchy PR (@anarchy_pr), we were given to opportunity to attend an advanced screening of the film. Michael McCauley (played by Liam Neeson), is an ex-cop, now insurance salesman, who is on his daily commute home C taking the metro train. A mysterious stranger (played by Vera Farmiga), offers him $100,000 if he identifies a hidden passenger on his train before the last stop. As he works against the clock to solve the puzzle, he realises he is caught in midst of a deadly criminal conspiracy and that his life and the lives of his fellow passengers are at risk. Does The Commuter manage to stay on track or does the movie get derailed before the credits roll? Check out what we thought in our review (we manage to keep it relatively spoiler-free until about the 10 minute mark). The Commuter opens officially in Australia on Thursday 18th January 2018. The Commuter (2018) Director: Jaume Collet-Serra Starring: Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga, Patrick Wilson, Sam Neill, Elizabeth McGovern 5.5 out of 10. It took three writers to come up with this movie's cliche-riddled script that borrows ideas from Murder on the Orient Express, Flightplan, Red Eye, countless Hitchcock films and even Neeson's previous starrer, Non Stop. Premise is unoriginal while the plot is hackneyed with very predictable bad guys. If you are a Neeson fan, this run-of-the-mill action-thriller will provide you a minor diversion, otherwise, wait for it on DVD or digital. #thecommuter #liamneeson #actionmovie #trainridetohell #train #whodunit

"Someone on this train does not belong." #TurpsFilmReview (6/10) THE COMMUTER is yet another collaboration between director Jaume Collet-Sera and Liam Neeson and is in the same vein as previous ventures, 'Unknown' and especially 'Non-Stop'. All three of these films revolve around a mystery that obviously isn't getting solved until the end. My biggest issue with this director (and his scripts) is that he never gives you enough context to solve these mystery films on your own, but then wants to pretend to be intelligent when you can't figure out "whodunit". There's virtually no shock value when you find out the culprit has been hiding off-screen for 99% of the movie. Non-Stop isn't quite as guilty as this film is, but it's just as manipulative in its approach. Collet-Sera just hides pertinent information to be revealed at the end in a really unsatisfactory way. The rest of the plot isn't special either and is entirely predictable. All the twists and turns can be seen from a mile away and character motives are pretty obvious right out of the gate. The reveal of why he was chosen by Vera Farmiga's character for this "experiment", or whatever you wanna call it, is completely ridiculous too. Liam Neeson almost single handedly saves this film from being 105 minutes of dullness with his performance. Say what you will, but Neeson is a master at holding your attention and could make eating a bowl cereal a thrill ride. The rest of the cast including Patrick Wilson, Sam Neill, Jonathan Banks, and Vera Farmiga are all serviceable and provide interesting enough characters. Overall however, THE COMMUTER took a decent idea and made a decent movie out of it. If you're a Neeson fan, there's enjoyment to be had here, but it's no 'Taken'. Thanks for reading.

It's been almost a decade since Liam Neeson played as Bryan Mills in Taken and that movie not only became a cult in class B action movie but also created a new sub-genre in action which is Neeson-genre. What is Neeson-genre? These are the movies starring Liam Neeson (of course lah!) as a messed-up/retired cop/ex-cop/agent that find redemption and escalate from zero to hero for the greater good in the movie. How can a generic plot like this become a genre with 9 movies since taken (taken trilogy, the grey, unknown, non-stop, a walk among the tombstones, run all night)? That is because he played as close as underdog he can be. There is no hi-tech weapon nor cool cars backing up. An old guy with sad puppy eyes, deep charismatic voice, a gun, a cellphone and a very particular self-skills to break some bones in a close combat and kick bad guys ass. That is my friends the deadly combination in Neeson-genre. The audience was entertained and the total box-office gross more than half a billion US dollars, not bad. (The production cost are very low for these movies) Back to the movies, as usual no spoiler spills but what I can tell you, according my eyes, this movie is a spiritual sequel of Non-stop. If in Non-stop we got Julliane Moore, in this movie we got The Warrens from Conjuring Franchise (Vera Varmiga & Patrick Wilson) face to face with Liam. There is some suspense like in Non-stop and because the setting in the train, I can't help it to compare with Murder at the Orient Express and yes, beside the glamorous Orient Express rather than NY Metro, this movie has more weight than the other one. For a Neeson-genre, this movie just got score 8/10 from me. A must watch movie for all commuters around jabodetabek just like myself 03

Udah nonton THE COMMUTER Dari awal THE COMMUTER emang mau dibikin seperti pendahulunya, NON-STOP (2014). Kedua film ini jadi berasa kembar, tapi ga identik. Yang satu bersetting di kereta, dan satu lagi di pesawat terbang. Secara genre pun sama. Action // Crime //Drama // Mystery // Thriller. Peran utama juga masih Liam Neeson, dan bangku sutradara juga masih dipegang Jaume Collet-Serra. Tapi sayangnya THE COMMUTER menurut gw ga sebagus NON-STOP. Gw lebih suka ketegangan yang disajikan NON-STOP. Gw lebih suka karakter Bill Marks (NON-STOP), ketimbang Michael MacCauley (THE COMMUTER). Gw lebih suka pendalaman semua karakter di NON-STOP. Dan udah pasti gw lebih suka cerita di NON-STOP. Kehadiran duo THE CONJURING (Vera Farmiga & Patrick Wilson) menurut gw belum bisa mengangkat film ini jadi lebih baik, pendalaman karakter mereka masih kurang (mungkin karena durasi mereka tampil sebentar), masih bagus mereka tampil di THE CONJURING. Tapi THE COMMUTER masih layak buat ditonton, terutama yang belum pernah nonton film NON-STOP, ga akan kecewa pastinya, masih enak ditonton & seru nebak-nebak siapa orang yang dicari diantara banyak penumpang. #TheCommuter #NonStop #LiamNeeson #BillMarks #MichaelMacCauley #VeraFarmiga #PatrickWilson

The January-February period is often filled with a ton of bad films, which is why it is considered as the 'cinematic wasteland' by established critics, but The Commuter is not one of them. This movie did not bring much new things to the table, but it did hit the right beats in providing a straightforward fun and entertaining action film. First of all, this movie surprisingly had a decent amount of urgency brought about by the fast, breakneck pacing of its story, which was balanced by some great level of suspense throughout. Liam Neeson really carried this movie well by just his mere presence on screen (what do you expect anyway?), and his performance managed to really give the film the tension and 'high stakes situation' feel it needed. The action sequences were also handled neatly and coherently with a ton of great wide shots and nice blend of CGI as well as without a lot of shaky cameras and quick cuts. My only issue with the movie was how it felt too familiar even for the action genre at times, but nevertheless it did not distract from the film much because I had fun with it for the most part. Overall, I would give The Commuter a B. It was certainly not a groundbreaking movie in any way, but it was a pretty good popcorn film that still deserves a checkout for your weekends. #jakarta #liamneeson #vsco #artwork #edit #movie #vscophile #filmmaking #filmphotography #lucasfilms #film #train #2017 #geek #thecommuter #hollywoodstudios #animation #singapore #acting #movies #films #bio #hollywoodmovies #techno #art #tim1912inthemovies #review #hollywood

Karina's review: The commuter is a movie that I feel is getting a little more hate than it deserves. The beginning of the movie was actually pretty good, it was interesting and mysterious. But it did have some pretty bad CGI and Questionable editing. I do feel that the connection with the main character really just wasn't there, so maybe they should've worked on the character development a little better. Also, the main character's family I had zero connection to at all, deffinetly could use a little backstory with all the characters. But the ending of the film lost me. I feel like it was unnecessary and a little over the top. There were things that just should have been left out of the film completely because they were completely unneeded. #TheCommuter (2018): 6/10 74 It’s ten years since Liam Neeson starred in Pierre Morel’s ‘Taken’, and yet, we still can’t seem to get enough of him in that kind of role. Neeson returns in his latest action flick The Commuter, which is pretty much ‘Non-Stop’ meets ‘Murder On The Orient Express’. Michael MacCauley (Neeson) is approached on his way home and seemingly threatened into finding someone on the train. 74 There are some nice effects and sweeping shots in the build-up from director Collet-Serra, but in truth we are all ready in waiting for Liam Neeson to spring into action as he so often does. The premise and overall plot are hardly groundbreaking, but the film is still entertaining on the whole. Where ‘Murder On The Orient Express’ attempted sophistication but ended up a little too slow, The Commuter hurtles along at a blistering, uncompromising pace. It’s classic Neeson of the last decade. 74 The Commuter will not be winning any awards any time soon, but then we never expected it to. That’s not why people will flock to see it. It’s good old fashioned entertainment. As long as you don’t read too much into the plot itself, such as how MacCauley is able to get away with killing so many people without so much as a ticking off, you’ll have a blast. #TheCommuter is a solid nearly two-hour action ride, that is better than you’d expect. In this film, a man on a commuter train is approached by a woman, and asked to complete a task that might end up with a passenger dead. Liam Neeson (“Taken”) is still kicking ass at his age, and making it look easy. An overall entertaining whodunnit that will leave you guessing until the very end. As much as we’ve all seen this formula before, this film still manages to be pretty decent. Go see it or wait to see it at home. 821582158215 . 61 Film Ini Ber-genre : Crime, Drama, Mysteri Film ini bercerita tentang Michael McCauley (Liam Neeson) adalah seorang pegawai asuransi yang hari itu sedang mengalami hari paling buruk dalam hidupnya. Sebagai kepala keluarga, ia adalah bapak yang bertanggung jawab. Kemudian Ia sedang mengalami masalah finansial untuk membayar registrasi kuliah anaknya dan mencoba untuk menyelesaikan masalah ini. Kemudian Michael masuk ke kantor dan menemukan bahwa karirnya selama sepuluh tahun sebagai pegawai teladan hilang begitu saja. Ia dipecat dan nasib kuliah anaknya berada di ujung tanduk. Dia bercerita kepada sahabatnya, Murphy (Patrick Wilson), bahwa ia belum berani mengatakan berita ini kepada istrinya. Ia belum tahu bagaimana caranya bertindak. Kemudian Michael masuk ke dalam komuter, transportasi hariannya selama sepuluh tahun terakhir, Ditengah perjalanan, seorang wanita misterius (Vera Farmiga) datang menghampiri dan meminta Michael mengungkap identitas penumpang tersembunyi di dalam kereta api sebelum pemberhentian terakhir. Michael kemudian menyadari sebuah rencana mematikan sedang berlangsung dan ia dijadikan alat dalam sebuah konspirasi kriminal yang dapat yang membahayakan nyawa dirinya dan sesama penumpang dalam kereta api tersebut. REVIEW MOVIE @thecommuterfilm ======== Tadinya ke bioskop pengen nonton #Flight555 ternyata masih coming soon dan tayang perdana hari ini gak masuk di Pontianak. Akhirnya lihat Opa Liam yang bertuliskan "from NON STOP Director", tahulah tuh film keren badai, secetar bulu mata Syahrini 09. Akhirnya fix nonton itu Awal-awal, oke! Aku anggap ini nggak sekeren Non Stop. Bertele-tele, banyak ngomong. Nggak kayak Non Stop yang langsung beraksi. Banyak adegan yang bisa dibuang sebenarnya Nah, selepas bertemu dengan Joanna ini di kereta, pleaseeee simak baik-baik guys. Inilah plot nya. Di sini kesamaan kayak NON STOP dimulai. Carilah dari ratusan penumpang kereta yang seharusnya gak ada di kereta itu. Kalau aku sih bisa garuk-garuk kepala lah Seperti di NON STOP, sekali lagi kita diajak nebak siapa yang gak pantas di kereta, dan siapa dalangnya? Gara-gara kesel 3x nebak orang salah di film NON STOP, gak berani spekulasi siapa. Karena siapapun berpotensi jadi antagonisnya. Awalnya curiga si xxx, eh kayaknya gak mungkin. [WEEKEND MOVIE] The Commuter ‘The Commuter’ merupakan film bergenre drama, crime dan mistery yang berasal dari Amerika. Sebagai sutradara film ini dipercayakan pada Jaume Collet-serra, berdasarkan skenario yang ditulis oleh Philip De Blasi dan Byron Willinger. ‘The Commuter’ diproduksi oleh Lionsgate, menampilkan bintang-bintang utamanya Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga, Sam Neill, Jonathan Banks, Elizabeth Mcgovern. Film ‘The Commuter’ bercerita tentang Michael (Liam Neeson) seorang salesman asuransi yang sedang melaksanakan perjalanan rutinnya. Di tengah perjalanan, seorang wanita misterius (Vera Farmiga) datang menghampiri dan meminta Michael mengungkap identitas penumpang tersembunyi di dalam kereta api sebelum pemberhentian terakhir. Michael kemudian menyadari sebuah rencana mematikan sedang berlangsung dan ia dijadikan ‘alat’ dalam sebuah konspirasi kriminal yang dapat membahayakan nyawanya dan penumpang lain dalam kereta tersebut. [Review film] Halo sob, to day i want to review movie yang berjudul "The Commuter" yang ditulis oleh Philip de Blasi and Byron Willinger dengan genre crime, drama, misteri. For the conflict, konflik difilm ini benar benar rumit dan very unpredictable. Jadi kalo kalian nontonnya sambil ngantuk ngantuk bakal susah banget untuk mendapatkan inti ceritanya. Dan genre drama di film ini tuh sangat sedikit sob, hanya sebatas keluarga Michael yang diteror oleh seseorang secret agent. Misteri di film ini bener bener bagus sekali, bahkan ini menjadi film yang bergenre misteri terbaik menurut reviewer. Untuk sens of humornya gak ada sob. Dan film ini thrillernya bener bener membuat jantungan. Untuk acting pemainnya kurang bagus, kenapa?, karena tokoh utamanya Michael (Liam Nesson) saat action kurang begitu bagus. Sangat disayangkan juga, karena inikan film yang bergenre crime ya sob, namun acting nya kurang maksimal. Untuk animation difilm ini bagus banget, apalagi saat kereta commuternya meledak di stasiun akhir, itu bener bener bagus banget. Pesan nya kurang nyampe sih sob menurut reviewer, paling hanya sebatas kasih sayang untuk keluarga saja. Dan film ini nyaris sama ceritanya seperti film yang berjudul "Murder on the Orient Express", but dont worry, misteri dan thrillernya bagus "The Commuter" hanya saja crimenya sejenus dengan "Murder on the Orient Express". Dan endingnya agak gak jelas sedikit sob, untuk mendapatkan siapa crime nya. 9999999999 The Commuter Part one of the Train Weekend Movie Marathon: Volume 2. I never thought I'd be doing a second Weekend Movie Marathon about trains. Apparently, there is a wide array of films taking place inside or having something to do with trains. Imagine this. You are sixty years old and you take the train to work every single day. The ride is long, yet that gives you enough time to make friends with other passengers. One day, however, you realize that this may be the last time you take the train because you have been fired from your job. Michael (Liam Neeson), an ex-cop, follows that exact routine for the last ten years, until he is fired. On what seems like him last time taking the train back home, Michael is approached by a mysterious woman who introduced herself as Joanna (Vera Farmiga). She makes a very tempting offer to Michael and asks him to do one simple thing: find a person that goes by the name Prynne, who's not a regular in this train. His reward will be twenty-five thousand dollars hidden inside the train and another seventy-five thousand when the job is complete. Michael finds the hidden money, which inadvertently makes him bound to see this request to the end. Being an ex-cop gives Michael the wits and resourcefulness to investigate in a limited amount of time and avoid all obstacles in his way, even the life-threatening ones. In all honesty, I am not a big fan of Liam Neeson. This, however, was a film that offers all that it promises: action, suspense, mystery, and some plot twists. Neither fast nor slow-paced, The Commuter is going to give you an exciting time watching it. The Commuter 7/10 Main cast : Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga What would happen if Hercule Point is played by Liam Neeson? Well that's what happens in this movie. Yes, the newest Liam Neeson action movie titled "the Commuter" is about an investigation with the added Liam Neeson style of action. Its just like "Nonstop" mixed with "Murder on Orient Express" The story is about a sales property agent that "randomly" meets a woman on the commuter who offers him something tempting. "What if I asked you to do something that would profoundly effect somebody on this train? Someone in this train is doesnt belong. All you have to do is find them" . Yes, that line explains what this movie is all about. From the beginning, the story is well structured. The background of the main character and why he is willing to accept that kind of offer builds with intensity until its climax. Many questions will pop out like "what actually happened?" , " who's the brains behind all of this". These all served greatly neat so "maybe u can't guess correctly". If u dont believe me, try to guess when you watch it. Just forget about logic ... consider this movie as just entertainment and you will enjoy it more because some of the scenes are unlogical and feel very set up but other then that, all great. About the cast, starting with Liam Neeson. He is in his comfort zone playing this kind of role so maybe you will find he's a lil bit boring. And Vera Farmiga, i like her though she doesn't appear much in this movie and feels like the Conjuring reunion because shes play with her "husband" Patrick Wilson. #movie #review #thecommuter #moviegoer #moviefreak #iamwhatiwatch

The commuter 7/10 Main cast : Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga Apa yang terjadi kalau hercule point diperankan oleh liam nesson? Well kalian bisa lihat itu di film ini. Yasss... film aksi terbaru liam nesson yang berjudul commuter ini mengangkat tema penyelidikan sebuah kasus atau teka teki dengan bumbu aksi ala liam nesson. Seperti nonton "nonstop" digabung dengan "murder on orient express". Bercerita tentang seorang agen sales properti yang secara "acak" bertemu dengan seorang wanita di sebuah commuter dan ditawari sebuah penawaran yang menggiurkan. "what if i ask you to do something that could performly affect individual on this train, someone on this train is dont belong. All you have to do is find them". Yah... itu adalah Sebuah pertanyaan yang mewakili keseluruhan cerita di film ini. Dari awal cerita dibangun dengan sangat baik, latar belakang tokoh utama dan berbagai alasan sampai ia "mau" melakukan pekerjaan itu dijelaskan terlebih dahulu sehingga membangun ketegangan yang intense sedikit demi sedikan sampai pada klimaksnya dan penonton akan dibuat bertanya tanya dari awal film apa yang terjadi? Siapa dibalik semua ini? Apa latar belakangnya? Dan semua itu semua itu disajikan dengan rapi dan tidak mudah ditebak. Kalau tidak percaya, coba kalian nonton dan tebaklah. Lupakan soal logika... anggap aja ini sebuah hiburan dan jika kalian melakukan itu kalian akan menikmati film ini karena ada beberapa adegan yang diluar akal sehat dan Terlalu banyak kebetulan seperti semua sudah diskenario. Tapi terlepas dari itu, film ini sangat menarik. Semua cast disini bermain dengan sangat baik dan memang tampaknya liam nesson belum bisa beranjak dari peran peran di zona nyamannya, sehinggal terasa sedikit membosankan. Lihat saja seperti "nonstop", atau "taken". Vera Farmiga bermain baik walau cuma muncul sedikit dan disini dia beradu akting lagi dengan "suaminya" patrick wilson. #movie #moviegoer #review #thecommuter

Hingga suatu hari ada seorang wanita mengajak melakukan permainan untuk menemukan seorang penumpang yang tidak seharusnya ada dikereta dengan iming-iming 100.000 dollar. Ternyata permainan ga cuma sekedar permainan karena menyangkut nyawa orang yang dicintai dan nyawa orang-orang diatas kereta. Diperankan oleh aktor lawas Liam Neeson. Bagi penggemar film action nama Liam Neeson tentu tidak asing. Acting pemain film Taken ini begitu apik. Intrik dan misterinya cukup membuat mata betah dilayar. Hanya saja actionnya kurang banyak. Tidak seperti difilm sebelumnya. Mampukah Liam Neeson menemukan orang yang dicarinya? Silahkan saksikan dibioskop kesayangan anda. Untuk penggemar film action drama sy sangat rekomendasikan. 61 C 61 The first 2/3 of this movie are awesome and fun - and then the last 3rd goes completely off the rails. The premise is genius: a man gets on his normal train home from work (after getting fired) and is told by a woman he'll get $100K if he finds the one person on the train who doesn't belong. I usually love thrillers with simple plots like this - and for a while it works. And then the last 30 minutes or so requires full abandonment of belief and physics and makes absolutely zero sense (also it's painfully obvious who the villain is from the beginning). Such a bummer because the initial idea is intense and intriguing - and then it all falls apart. I love Liam Neeson but this was clearly just a paycheck. #thecommuter #liamneeson

Movie Night : THE COMMUTER @cinema.21 City Of Tommorow Studio 3 Row H Seat 11 My Movie Meters : 8/10 Someone on this train does not belong In the Tradition of Non Stop and Run All Night, with a bit of Agatha Christie's Mystery Formula, The Commuter is a thrill ride one action package that not to be missed It' was Nice to see Vera Farmiga (Bates Motel) and Patrick Wilson (Angels in America) together in a movie again, a truly Conjuring Reunion and both played as a villain this time, a rare case for them , Patrick however did once in Hard Candy Mr Neeson still got it, the fight the action the drama, glad he still land on a big major pictures, unlike our friend Mr Willis who mostly stuck on B Action movie nowadays Almost 80% of the movie took place in a Commuter train, but there's no room fo boredom, the mystery and the action is Super race pace, for the ice breaker the director did put a bit comedy and a funny moments, it's Murder on The Commuter with Conspiracy and Cat and Mouse chase , the culprit is the least of we suspected So next time you're on a Commuter, be very careful and don't be greedy, just sit on the corner be silent as a Ninja waiting for your station stop, never talk to strangers My CinemaScore : A 8282828293 #TheCommuter #LiamNeeson #VeraFarmiga #PatrickWilson #Action #CinemaXXI #Cito #CityOfTommorow #MovieOfTheWeek #moviereview #SoManyMoviesSoLittleTime #BestTimeSpentIsWithMoviesAndBooks

Film : The Commuter (2018) BAGI KALIAN YANG SUDAH MENONTON SILAKAN MEMBERIKAN PENDAPAT TERSENDIRI! Sinopsis : bercerita tentang seorang pria bernama Michael McCauley (Liam Nesson) yang sehari-harinya menggunakan transportasi Commuter sebagai penunjang pekerjaannya, salesman asuransi. Ketegangan dimulai ketika Michael bertemu dengan seorang wanita misterius, Joanna (Vera Farmiga) yang menghampirinya dan meminta Michael mengungkap identitas penumpang tersembunyi di dalam kereta api sebelum pemberhentian terakhir ketika perjalanan pulangnya dari kantor. Review : Bagi penonton setia dari serial movie Liam Neeson sangat penasaran dengan film ini dan udah bisa di tebak THE COMMUTER itu ibarat NON-STOP 2.. Film ini bagus ko bahkan jalan cerita HAMPIR SERUPA dengan NON-STOP tapi dari segi penceritaan tergolong Sedikit rumit. Film ini tidak berusaha keras menjadi film cerdas dengan misterinya dan kita cukup duduk dan menikmati jalan cerita tanpa pusing2 memikirkan MISTERINYA karena TWIST si penjahatnya nya akan terbuka seiring jalan cerita, sekali lagi persis dengan dengan jalan cerita di NON-STOP Actionnya cukup bagus meskipun si Opa sudah tua, Kasian Dipukul Pukul.. :( Kekurangan : LIAM NESSON memerankan karakter gitu lagi gitu lagi, cek aja semua film2 kolaborasi dengan sutradara karakternya setipe, kalo ga polisi ya ex-polisi, jago berantem, ga jelek sih cuman udah BASI. seperti ane bilang Konflik dan jalan cerita udah terlalu sering di bikin HOLLYWOOD. jika NON-STOP karakter LIAM NESSON di beri "tugas" yang twistnya merupakan balas dendam. maka ini dengan tujuan KONSPIRASI. Kesimpulan: Cukup menghibur buat penghilang lelah setelah balik kerja. As usual I didn't watch the trailer for this movie, I don't like watching trailers for movies because I want the movie going experience to be a suprise. I only saw the poster before going into the movie, there was a statement that stated "from the director of Non-Stop and The Shallows". To summarize this movie, This movie was basically Non-Stop all over again except this time it's Liam Neeson on a train. I could see someone enjoying this movie if they haven't seen Non-Stop but for me it was so predictable from start to finish. There are some ridiculously implausible scenes that would fit perfectly in a Fast and Furious movie. I did find some parts of this movie to be enjoyable at times, like Liam Neeson kicking ass despite constantly feeling like it's a rethread of Non-Stop and a number of other movies. As far as January movies go it's decent entertainment.

The Commuter Nonton film "The Commuter" ini berasa seperti hari-hari gw naik kereta berangkat dan pulang kerja difilmkan. Bedanya, gw gak terlibat dalam konspirasi kejahatan seperti yang dialami oleh Michael MacCauley dalam perjalanan pulang menuju Cold Spring. Film yang dibintangi oleh Liam Neeson dan Vera Farmiga ini menurut gw cukup memberikan banyak pertanyaan di benak gw yang perlahan terbangun dari awal Michael naik kereta. Kenapa harus Michael yang terpilih untuk mencari tau satu penumpang bernama "Prynne" diantara ratusan penumpang di kereta? Ada banyak "pengawas" di kereta, kenapa bukan mereka aja yang cari Prynne? Michael ini termasuk penumpang yang menurut gw cukup kepo dengan urusan penumpang lain. Sehingga dia bisa hafal siapa saja orang yang naik kereta barengan dengan dia di jam yang sama selama 10 tahun terakhir. Semakin berumur, Liam Neeson makin sering memainkan peran sebagai bapak bijak dan baik juga kepala keluarga yang tangguh. Gw suka semangatnya di film ini. ★★★ #thecommuter

(Listen / download) That Film Stew Ep 103 - The Commuter Review (LINK IN BIO) The action thriller The Commuter is directed by Jaume Collet-Serra, and stars Liam Neeson, Vera Farmiga, Patrick Wilson, Jonathan Banks, Elizabeth McGovern, and Sam Neil. Thanks to Anarchy PR (@anarchy_pr), we were given to opportunity to attend an advanced screening of the film. Michael McCauley (played by Liam Neeson), is an ex-cop, now insurance salesman, who is on his daily commute home C taking the metro train. A mysterious stranger (played by Vera Farmiga), offers him $100,000 if he identifies a hidden passenger on his train before the last stop. As he works against the clock to solve the puzzle, he realises he is caught in midst of a deadly criminal conspiracy and that his life and the lives of his fellow passengers are at risk. Does The Commuter manage to stay on track or does the movie get derailed before the credits roll? Check out what we thought in our review (we manage to keep it relatively spoiler-free until about the 10 minute mark). The Commuter opens officially in Australia on Thursday 18th January 2018.
